Debuilder
=========

Dependencies
------------

- rebuildd
- inoticoming

Install
-------

make prefix=/usr sysconfdir=/etc localstatedir=/var install

Configure
---------

Edit /etc/debuilder/config

addgroup debuilder
chgrp debuilder /var/spool/debuilder
chmod 775 /var/spool/debuilder

Run
---

Run as a root:

  debuilder-configure # This is needed only once
  debuilder

Usage
-----

  debuilder-copy-pkg anypackage_1.0-1.dsc # User must belong to debuilder group
